: "1193463555988243", "uri": "https://scontent-ord5-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/491821725_1193463559321576_4631848987853923115_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=b66uMiH4NOEQ7kNvwFaFPKy&_nc_oc=AdkelCerBC-eCAvBodBb-QPpmV6s_4zHIRxdZRHiWSdYtnkNVQyQvFi6fPQ6jh44FOo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_Afks69rHHctIOPVasyUkushlbblXZM8CRjmX51uttDpyjw&oe=69454237"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Forever Pets key art 4 2560px x 1440px.png", "id": "1737682920453810", "uri": "https://scontent-ord5-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/491821674_1737682923787143_6829752738076224590_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=RUqumrV_-UkQ7kNvwFS_lNX&_nc_oc=AdkFXlQUNDOePlID3lv0Q_x9GSGXb8Fka04M8-bEmc0RZcg2OjH0cC3gjlUUOeBaKAA&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AfmbGE6h3vqnN0e2fSPdKS35BHiAwpkzrA9gUE11yw9ghg&oe=69452A1D"}, "display_name": "Forever Pets", "keywords": ["pet", "cozy", "bird", "cat", "cats"], "long_description": "# **Love, Play, Bond - Like Never Before!**\n\n**Forever Pets is more than a pet simulator.** It's a heartfelt sanctuary **crafted for animal lovers and anyone seeking joy, peace, and genuine connection.**\n\n{2212525485905859}\n\nStep into a warm, interactive world where your care brings adorable pets to life and their unique personalities fill your days with wonder. **Experience a real bond** with pets that react to your touch, voice and care in an authentic way.\n\n{1691179851840497}\n\n**Adopt** from a growing collection of unique cats and birds.\n{1471839667251162}\n\n**Hatch baby birds** and watch them grow every single day.\n\n{2752166874986789}\n\n**Enjoy dynamic play** where you and your pets interact and play together as a family.\n{1545670800086910}\n\n**Discover unique personalities** with their own likes and dislikes.\n\n{3714638302004482}\n\n**Play fun mini-games** to boost their skills and your own.\n\n{823939393884173}\n\n**Style** your pets with adorable accessories and watch them show off their new look with happiness and unique coolness.\n\n{2043093636443802}\n\n**Play board games** with Dr. Pixel and friends soon, **with your pets curled up beside you**.\n\n{1936766413938593}\n\n# **Forever Pets** Isn\u2019t Just a Game\n\nIt's a journey of nurturing, a source of daily calm, and a celebration of the small moments that bring the greatest happiness. \n\n{2349929148757988}\n\n# **Your Adventure Starts Now!**\n\nThis is just the beginning - stay tuned for more mini-games, deeper interactions, and a growing collection of pets to love.\n\n", "short_description": "Forever Pets is your sanctuary for genuine connection. Adopt and raise lifelike cats and birds in an unscripted world. Enjoy delightful moments of group play where you all interact as a family. Watch their personalities shine as they grow daily. Play skill-boosting mini-games together, and style them with accessories they'll proudly show off. Play board games alongside Dr. Pixel and friends, your pets always by your side. This is more than a game - it's a heartfelt journey of nurturing and joy. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://virtualbeings.notion.site/Privacy-Policy-for-Forever-Pets-23bcee78bb838043add5d84de84bc45e?source=copy_link", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Virtual Beings SAS", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.virtualbeings.co/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1990104051447093"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["HAND_TRACKING"