Afn4mPOdHc5ZBogsbYUsvcW0WI-Kucpn5vuID2qluGQi5Q&oe=69453312"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Forever Pets key art 4 2560px x 1440px.png", "id": "1737682920453810", "uri": "https://scontent-ord5-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/491821674_1737682923787143_6829752738076224590_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=RUqumrV_-UkQ7kNvwFS_lNX&_nc_oc=AdkFXlQUNDOePlID3lv0Q_x9GSGXb8Fka04M8-bEmc0RZcg2OjH0cC3gjlUUOeBaKAA&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AfmbGE6h3vqnN0e2fSPdKS35BHiAwpkzrA9gUE11yw9ghg&oe=69452A1D"}, "display_name": "Forever Pets", "keywords": ["pet", "simulation", "cozy", "bird", "family"], "long_description": "# **Forever Pets : Love, Play, Bond - Like Never Before!**\n\n**Adopt, nurture, and fall in love** with your very own virtual pets in this heartwarming VR experience - crafted for animal lovers and anyone seeking joy, peace, and connection. From hatching baby birds to guiding them through life\u2019s adventures, your care shapes their growth, and their love enriches yours.\n\n# **Nurture Lifelike Virtual Pets**\n\nYour pets **react to your touch, voice, and care -** feeding, grooming, and teaching them tricks feels wonderfully real. Watch them grow from cautious hatchlings into confident companions.\n{2069837857155063}\n\n# **Play, Learn & Thrive Together**\n\nStrengthen your bond through **playful learning & mini-games** like musical challenges and bubble popping, or share mindful moments - stretching, breathing, and exercising side by side for joy and calm.\n{1262448362199946}\n\n# **Unwind in Your Peaceful Retreat**\n\nEnjoy quiet moments with your pets - from sunlit naps to board games with **Dr. Pixel**, your wise robotic mentor (who even brings gifts!). Let **KUBO** assist as you bond, creating perfect harmony between play and relaxation.\n{776274151423208}\n\n# **Forever Pets** Isn\u2019t Just a Game\n\nIt\u2019s a haven of love, a celebration of growth, and a reminder that the smallest bonds can bring the greatest happiness.\n\n# **This is Just the Beginning!**\n\nStart your journey with adorable birds in Early Access, and stay tuned - cats are coming next!\n\n# **Ready to Meet your Forever Friend?**", "short_description": "Hatch a baby bird and raise your new companion in Forever Pets, a magical VR experience where your care helps the little one grow. Feed, train, and play together to unlock joyful mini-games and deepen your bond. Watch your bird learn to fly, rest when tired, and thrive with your love. When it's time to relax, enjoy board games with Dr. Pixel, your cheerful robot friend. A heartfelt journey of growth and connection awaits."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://virtualbeings.notion.site/Privacy-Policy-for-Forever-Pets-23bcee78bb838043add5d84de84bc45e?source=copy_link", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Virtual Beings SAS", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://virtualbeings.notion.site/Forever-Pets-a-VR-game-by-VIRTUAL-BEINGS-23bcee78bb83802eab3adf901b551da2?source=copy_link", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "331529188132278"}, {"id": "1676485315806614"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "30542704465375467"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1894012414886228"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1894012414886228"}, "is_approved": true, "firstO